Instantiations of class template normal_distribution model a  random distribution . Such a distribution produces random numbers x distributed with probability density function   $\displaystyle p(x) =
  \frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}\sigma} e^{-\frac{(x-\mu)^2}{2\sigma^2}}
$$\displaystyle p(x) =
  \frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}\sigma} e^{-\frac{(x-\mu)^2}{2\sigma^2}}
$, where mean and sigma are the parameters of the distribution.

